{"tid":2407503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中英媒體戰！英撤CGTN環球電視網執照 德國跟進","createTime":"2021-02-14T05:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T06:30:41.000Z","uid":3197,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7c2f26bc26c1dd7e55cea72a7de25d73ef8786d3","tid":2407503,"uid":3197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T05:53:35.000Z","msg":"英國撤銷大陸官媒中國環球電視網（CGTN）的播放執照後，德國也將依據歐洲多個國家間的共用牌照協議，禁止CGTN在德國播出。CGTN在歐洲停播的效應恐將進一步擴大。<br />\n<br />\n據德國之聲中文網報導，德國北威州媒體管理局在12日證實這項消息。本月4日英國通訊管理局（Ofcom）吊銷CGTN的播出牌照，根據歐洲1989年的「跨境電視」協議，CGTN因為在英國獲得播出許可，因此便自動獲准在德國播出。而在英國Ofcom取消播出牌照之後，CGTN在德國的播放許可也同時失效。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.co.uk/amp/s/udn.com/news/amp/story/121996/5250015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.co.uk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Fstory%2F121996%2F5250015&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=8668387d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.co.uk/amp/s/udn.com/news/amp/story/121996/5250015</a>"},{"pid":"67abad416732f8169a517ee3ac565188a9236552","tid":2407503,"uid":25673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T06:30:41.000Z","msg":"等胡狗出嚟吠"}]}